data.description:
Desirable Fox Farm area Home located in quiet cul-de-sac! This home features 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms and 2
car garage, vaulted ceilings and hardwood througout main floor living room and kitchen, new carpet and all new windows/sliders in 2019. Close to Meadowlark Elementary, multiple parks, airport and shopping! Deck off kitchen and primary bedroom with large backyard that is fully fenced and offers ample room for play, gardening and entertainment. For more information contact Mark Blades at 406-799.0030 or your Real Estate Professional.
